# AWS Services with Reservation Models

## Doc
* [Pricing for Provisioned Capacity](https://aws.amazon.com/dynamodb/pricing/provisioned/)

## Acronym
* RDS - Relational Database Service

## List
1) Amazon EC2
2) Amazon RDS
3) Amazon Redshfit
4) Amazon ElastiCache
5) Amazon DynamoDB

