## DynamoDB Reservation Model
1) On-demand
  * Automatically adjusts 
  * Charged per million
  * Based on actual use
  * Good for irregular or low-volume workloads
2) Provisoned
  * Specify capacity
  * Charged hourly
  * Changes with capacity
  * Good for periodic predictable workloads
3) Reserved
  * Specify 100-unit blocks
  * Upfront + reduced rate
  * Charged constantly
  * Good for constant predictable workloads
